{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a4b8350e21","title":"中央军委对冲击广州军区各造反派的命令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"61ea623b5d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":8,"articleId":"a4b8350e21","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央军委文件","id":"d125b2a9b6","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f2f051ef57","type":"title","text":"中央军委对冲击广州军区各造反派的命令","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7fb698d58","type":"paragraph","text":"命令（一）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13cb3a5686","type":"paragraph","text":"军队院校和文艺团体的同志们：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d840c892d","type":"paragraph","text":"我人民解放军应该坚决捍卫和执行最高指示，坚决执行军委命令。昨晚部分同志冲击广州军区领导机关和无命令自由抓人打人，是直接违犯毛主席批发的军委八项命令的，是一种错误行为。广州军区坚决维护军委命令，是完全正确的。希望你们分清是非，立即离开军区机关营区。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ab2357502","type":"paragraph","text":"地方各革命组织和革命师生同志们：昨晚所发生的事情，纯属于军队内部的事情，请你们不要介入。请你们自觉捍卫毛XX批发的军委八项命令，立即离开军队营区。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5bb2de0c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fb89ae4d6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年二月八日十七时三十分","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cad073197e","type":"paragraph","text":"命令（二）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dee0199494","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.02.08","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0492b533e4","type":"paragraph","text":"一、军队院校师生和文艺团体的同志们：今天下午十七时三十分军委已经下了命令，要你们坚决执行毛XX批发的军委八条命令，你们没有执行，现再命令你们立即撤退。你们有什么问题，可以立即向北京打电话或派代表来北京解决。否则，一切后果由你们负责。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f99febdfbd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、地方各革命组织和革命师生同志们：广州面临港澳，情况非常复杂，希望你们提高警惕，不要介入这场冲击，应该坚决拥护最高统帅的八条命令。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26d324d975","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91db1e0d83","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年二月八日二十时三十分","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a4b8350e21","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}